    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <opener><dateline/><salute>Dear Sir</salute></opener>
                
                <p>M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Mostyn performed to a miracle &amp; does His tutors vast 
                    honor.<note type="editorial">In view of the reference to 
                        'tutors', this probably refers to 
                        a young member of the Mostyn family, possibly <persName ref="pe0414">Thomas Mostyn</persName>, born in 1776.</note> at request of 
                    M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Falconer &amp; me he permits you to give us y<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> company too 
                    morrow.<note type="editorial">This may refer to <persName ref="pe1119">Thomas Falconer</persName> rather than to Pennant's brother-in-law
                        (from his first marriage), <persName ref="pe0390">Revd James Falconer</persName>.</note> I have provided 
                    Keffel<note type="editorial">'Horse'.</note>
                    so send boots, &amp; Baggage &amp;c by Bearer &amp; follow yrself. with all speed. I have just had a most irritating Letter
                    about <placeName ref="pl1338">Penmaen mawr</placeName> so we must 
                    defend ourselves<note type="editorial">Cf. E. R. Owen's letter of 4 September 1782 to Pennant,
                        which corrects 'some misinformation respecting Penmaen-mawr',
                        in NLW 2594E, Caernarvonshire folder.</note> 
                </p> 
                <closer><salute>y<hi rend="superscript">rs</hi> &amp;c</salute>
                    <signed><persName ref="pe0232">T. Pennant</persName></signed>
                    <dateline>June 9<hi rend="superscript">th</hi></dateline></closer>
            </div>
            <div><p><address><addrLine>To<lb/>The <persName ref="pe0333">Rev<hi rend="superscript">d</hi> M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Lloyd</persName><lb/>
                <placeName ref="pl1201">Caerwis</placeName>.</addrLine></address></p>
            </div>
        </body>
